show.description: Five years ago, she had a one-night stand and became pregnant, only to find out later that the man wasn't her fiancé as she thought. After being kicked out of her home, she became a single mother. When she returned to the city with her twins, she was shocked to discover that her boss, the cold billionaire, was the father of her children
